105
00:04:57,299 --> 00:04:59,020
will be on the rise.

106
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:00,700
Dr. Qin,

107
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,659
all these years, for Miss Mi,

108
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:04,700
