120
00:05:37,859 --> 00:05:38,824
You still remember it?

121
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:41,060
I mean, if...

122
00:05:42,099 --> 00:05:43,180
If I want to see a rainbow

123
00:05:44,099 --> 00:05:45,140
