126
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:52,712
A rainbow?

127
00:05:53,940 --> 00:05:54,824
In a glass house?

128
00:06:02,299 --> 00:06:03,979
From a common sense perspective,

129
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,339
