130
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:08,500
It's formed by water
and sunlight together.

131
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,740
At first hearing,
it's elusive, intangible,

132
00:06:12,219 --> 00:06:14,020
and indeed somewhat unrealistic.

133
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:17,140
